snippet.title: EGG BONDA | MUTTAI BONDA | Road Side Evening Snacks Recipe Cooking In Village | Bajji Street Food
snippet.description:
In this video, we bring you the ultimate recipe for Egg Bonda (Muttai Bonda), a beloved roadside evening snack that everyone enjoys! Watch as we prepare this crispy, golden-brown delight in a traditional village setting, using fresh ingredients and time-honored cooking techniques.

The Egg Bonda is made by coating perfectly boiled eggs with a spiced gram flour batter and frying them to perfection. This mouthwatering snack is best enjoyed hot, with an evening. Whether you're a fan of street food or looking for a quick and tasty recipe to try at home, this video has you covered!

Get a glimpse of authentic village-style cooking and join us as we prepare this classic Indian snack in a scenic, peaceful atmosphere.

snippet.title: Charche - Xvir Grewal & Dhanda Nyoliwala (Music Video) | Deepesh Goyal | VYRL Haryanvi
snippet.description:
Watch the groundbreaking collaboration that brings together the best of Punjab and Haryana in a rap extravaganza as ever rising Dhanda Nyoliwala joins forces with Xvir Grewal for a one-of-a-kind Punjabi-Haryanvi track.

Listen to Charche on:

Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/7a3QGSVDPG5NHTXKuZVurS?si=906bc7f0fea446aa
Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/us/album/charche/1789944518?i=1789944519
JioSaavn: https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/charche/XSMAdRlmYgA

Make your reels: https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1864907074313373/

#VYRLHaryanvi #Charche #DhandaNyoliwala 

Audio Credits:
Singer, Lyrics, Composer: Xvir Grewal, Dhanda Nyoliwala
Music: Romeoz
Mix Master: Ashock
Project by: Sumit Bamal

Video Credits:
Director: Deepesh Goyal
DOP: Vikcee
AD: Amit Syal, Ankit Thapa
Editor/DI: Bharat Mittal/Deepesh Goyal
DOP Asst.: Rahul Sabharwal
Operator: Rupi
Asst.: Pawan Kumar

EP: Raja

VFX: KP VFX Studios
CGI/3D: Parryfied
Foley: Apsy Singh
Design: Sumit Bamal

Music release inquiries: contact.vyrlregional@umusic.com 

Lyrics:

Gaddi shookdi hi jaave
Munda 150 te laave
Naal 4 yaar khas
Keda sanu hath laave
Dur bitcha toh snitcha toh
Life sohni saari jaave
Jaan kaala kaala yaara di yaari te karche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche
Obvious ae gaal saade hone charche
Hunda vi ae hone vi ae saade charche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche


Baade rooh de rangeen Munde 
Att de shaukeen Munde 
Gaal hove ankhan di
Saade bad scene hunde
Sire de ae dith
Tappe saadi leek
Fer malo mali malo mali malo mali
Sir  chad jaande parche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche
Obvious ae gaal saade hone charche
Hunda vi ae hone vi ae saade charche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche

Tu beeta hua kal
Mera flow jaise Future 
Underground chalu jaise mein
Mewat ka koi Buchter
Jo bars meri week thi 
Vo tere liye tutor hai 
Tu ankh band kre baitha jaise koi kabootar hai
 Gangster sune mere gaane baithe jail mein
Mein Dm Nahi krta bars karu mail mein
Naam k hi rapper hai yeah sun tu detail mein
Labelo pe dekhe hai zameer inke sale mein
Luck te nahi khade hai hukk the
Mein Fuck na deyu Koi deta jo takht pe
Vakht hai mera inki jamante japt hai
Mere doore Dhari inki amante girvi
Inke pale daale kuch ni 
Yeah baat maare fir bhi
Jind k julane tak
Delhi k buwane tak
Naam le diye tu tanne pahochade tikane tak
Maa duae mere sath hai sath hai 
Oh sikra mein guddi kya baat hai baat hai
Bhai kisse ka digaya nahi digda mein
Jab tak sar pr bhole ka mere hath hai hath hai
Ehna hoya ni siyana 
Har cheez te mein bola
Kaam di ae bukh fame da ni rola
Buss dekhi chalo jatt kidda thal de barola
Jurta naa jande ae takh palte
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche
Obvious ae gaal saade hone charche
Hunda vi ae hone vi ae saade charche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche

Recently, Dr. Kumar Vishwas has started hosting energy sessions popularly Known as Apne Apne Ram and Apne Apne Shyam where he talks about life skills of Shri Ram‚Äôs and Shri Krishna's life, and the applicability of the same in one‚Äôs own life to over come the challenges and social concerns we come across in our life.

Ho main to jhoom jhoom ke gaau re..

yaar da phira,

Udta gulaal hoke
Uski hi nazre utaar da phira.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS |  Real Madrid 5-2 Celta de Vigo | Copa del Rey 2024/25
snippet.description:
Real Madrid made it through to the quarter-finals of the Copa del Rey, overcoming Celta in a hard-fought match that was settled in extra time thanks to Endrick‚Äôs brace and another from Valverde. Earlier, our team had taken a 2-0 lead after a stunning finish from Mbapp√© and another from Vini Jr. However, the Galicians equalised in the final minutes through Bamba and Marcos Alonso from the penalty spot. On January 20th, Ancelotti's side will learn who their opponent will be in the next round of the competition.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

 The 8th Pay Commission, recently approved by the Union Cabinet ahead of the 2025 budget, is set to revise the salaries of nearly 50 lakh central government employees. This commission will not only result in salary hikes but also an adjustment in the Dearness Allowance (DA). While the exact percentage of salary hikes remains unclear, reports suggest that the fitment factor could rise from 2.57 to 2.86, which could lead to significant increases in basic pay. The new commission follows previous pay revisions under the 7th, 6th, and 5th Pay Commissions, each of which has adjusted government employee pay scales based on factors like inflation, the economy, and income disparities. Learn how pay commissions impact salaries and what employees can expect in the upcoming 8th Pay Commission.

Telegram link - https://web.telegram.org/k/#@indepthdrishtiias    

 The 8th Pay Commission, recently approved by the Union Cabinet ahead of the 2025 budget, is set to revise the salaries of nearly 50 lakh central government employees. This commission will not only result in salary hikes but also an adjustment in the Dearness Allowance (DA). While the exact percentage of salary hikes remains unclear, reports suggest that the fitment factor could rise from 2.57 to 2.86, which could lead to significant increases in basic pay. The new commission follows previous pay revisions under the 7th, 6th, and 5th Pay Commissions, each of which has adjusted government employee pay scales based on factors like inflation, the economy, and income disparities. Learn how pay commissions impact salaries and what employees can expect in the upcoming 8th Pay Commission.
